{"word":"G2618 - κατακαίω - katakaíō - kat-ak-ah'-ee-o - Burn up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατακαίω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katakaíō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ak-ah'-ee-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Burn up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சுட்டெரி, வெந்துபோ, எரிந்துபோ"},{"paragraph":"to burn up, consume by fire"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G2545 - καίω - kaíō - kah'-yo/2545\">G2545</a>; to <i>burn down</i> (to the ground), that is, <i>consume wholly:</i> - burn (up, utterly).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}